verbose_text: Data show that LRRK2 gradually, yet significantly increased with age in the PD-LRRK2- (healthy control; R = 0.52, p = 0.0044; XREF_FIG) and the PD+ LRRK2+ groups (R = 0.57, p = 0.037) but not in the PD-LRRK2+ (XREF_FIG) or PD+ LRRK2- groups (XREF_FIG).
